%% Diagram: Observer Lifecycle
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart TB
  N["new IntersectionObserver(callback, options)"] --> O["observe(target)"]
  O --> U["Async intersection updates"]
  U --> C["callback(entries)"]
  C --> M{"Continue?"}
  M -->|"keep observing"| U
  M -->|"one target done"| X["unobserve(target)"]
  X --> U
  M -->|"teardown"| D["disconnect()"]
